# game/Scenes/Jez/JezDates/jezluigisdate.rpy:29
translate french jezluigisstartdate_ec0fa6ca:

    # "I meet Jez at Luigi's and we sit and order our meals."
    "Je retrouve Jez chez Luigi's, on s'assoit et on commande notre repas."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezDates/jezluigisdate.rpy:30
translate french jezluigisstartdate_c57a5228:

    # "Then we chat for a while."
    "Puis on discute un moment."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezDates/jezluigisdate.rpy:33
translate french jezluigisstartdate_0875967f:

    # "The server brings our food out, and we continue talking while we eat."
    "Le serveur nous apporte notre repas, et on continue à parler tout en mangeant."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezDates/jezluigisdate.rpy:35
translate french jezluigisstartdate_3c0f7991:

    # "When we're done eating, we just hang around and talk for a while longer."
    "Une fois qu'on a fini de manger, on reste là à discuter encore un peu."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezDates/jezluigisdate.rpy:38
translate french jezluigisstartdate_e9a5d339:

    # "We could probably sit and chat all night, but it's starting to get late."
    "On pourrait probablement rester assis à bavarder toute la nuit, mais il commence à se faire tard."

